Subject: AIC Console error message after database migration
Description:
AIC Console error message after database migration.

Stealthaudit database has been migrated to a new SQL server. The storage settings have been updated to the new SQL server. Now the web portal access tab is throwing an error message.

"Unable to contact the SQL server database"
What_We_Know__c: AIC was not modified to use the new database. We fixed the database to point at the new location and the issue is resolved.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue:
AIC console is not responding or opening after upgrading NEA.

Cause:
AIC did not get updated with new database information leading to a failure to connect to the back end database.

Resolution:
Re installation allowed us to reconfigure the database to the correct settings, allowing AIC to start.
